Package: scatter
Title: Scatterplots with descriptive statistics
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: person("Piotr", "Tompalski", email = "piotr.tompalski@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides tools for creating scatterplots to compare observed and predicted values, with optional agreement metrics displayed as annotations. 
    The plots support grouped data and faceting.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.1),
    yardstick,
    ggplot2,
    ggtext
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    stringr,
    scales
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
URL: https://ptompalski.github.io/scatter/
